Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.60,0:08:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很擔心的眼神看我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}she's really worried about it, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.67,0:08:48.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這你不能怪她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, I don't blame her, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.65,0:08:50.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的狀態就像你胳膊上紋得一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, you are, as you say on your arm,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.87,0:08:52.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛是著魔了  對吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it's like obsessed, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.79,0:08:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很難說清  別人可能會以為\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know, just as if you might be
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.58,0:08:56.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你正在經歷中年危機\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}going through a bit of a midlife crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:09:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎  我暈  什么狗屁中年危機\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Really? Bloody hell! Midlife crisis, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我承認  她說的有些話讓我驚訝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I must admit, I was surprised by some of the stuff she said,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.25,0:09:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是那句中年危機\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}especially when she said, midlife crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.66,0:09:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人們會這樣想嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is that what people are thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.33,0:09:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我來說這很正常\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To me it's just normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.59,0:09:13.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是喜歡紋身  紋的是我喜歡的東西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's just something that I'm doing and it's something that I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.31,0:09:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我紋好這一個以后  我可能會想著\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So when I get this tattoo done, I'll be thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是最后一個了吧  可露西說了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll make this the last one. Lucy says, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.31,0:09:18.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得了吧  怎么可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please, your last one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.89,0:09:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些言論沒有改變我的任何想法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's not turned me in any way
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.19,0:09:22.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或是讓我再重新考慮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}into having second thoughts or anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.16,0:09:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只會覺得  人們就是這種反應\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I just think, oh, right, that's the reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.13,0:09:26.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以理解\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right, that's fair enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.44,0:09:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那好吧  再見\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right then, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.86,0:09:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-回見  -拜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- OK, yeah. - Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.54,0:09:35.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在伯明翰的尖矛工作室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In Spear Studio, Birmingham,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.36,0:09:37.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙蘭·貝利是那里的常客\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}one of their regulars, Fran Bailey,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.27,0:09:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她大老遠從威爾士的新市鎮過來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}has come all the way from New Town, Wales
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.42,0:09:42.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想進一步完善她的獨特設計\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}for some more work on her unique project.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.46,0:09:44.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我剛剛失去今年的第五只貓咪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've just lost my fifth cat in a year
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.91,0:09:49.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是我將它們的畫像紋在自己的背上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and I'm having their portraits put on my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.49,0:09:52.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愛貓勝過一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I love cats more than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.77,0:09:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貓咪是最美好的生靈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Cats are the bestest thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.16,0:09:57.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是狗  我和別人的想法不同\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not dogs, like other people seem to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:09:58.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面朝那邊可以嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you want to face that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.68,0:09:59.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:05.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望我的貓咪與眾不同\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wanted something that was a bit different with my cats,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.92,0:10:07.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,展現出它們的個性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and showed off their personalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中間的斯波克先生總是弄傷自己\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr Spock, he's in the middle and he was always hurting himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.04,0:10:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它渾身貼滿繃帶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}so he's got loads of bandages all over him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.72,0:10:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刷子先生戴單片眼鏡系著領結\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr Brush has got a monocle and a bow tie,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為它是典型的英倫紳士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}because he was a very English gentleman,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.88,0:10:25.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是它其實試圖統治世界\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but he was also set on world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.74,0:10:27.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有汀琪  它是我的寶貝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's Tinky, who was my baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我是只貓咪  又是拉拉的話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If I was a cat and a lesbian,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:33.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它就是我的真名天喵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that would be the cat for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:34.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要嫁給這只喵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd marry that cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.88,0:10:37.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好愛這只貓咪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I loved that cat so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.71,0:10:42.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙蘭找到了綜合這兩種愛好的方法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And Fran's found a way of combining both her passions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.97,0:10:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪  看起來好亮眼  一級棒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh my god! It looks so bright! That's ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.06,0:10:48.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一點點地方需要重做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just got little bits to redo at some point,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.71,0:10:50.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這里  還有這里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}like there and up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.09,0:10:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在她父母的家里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Back at her parents' house,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙蘭將她的舊臥室改裝成了紋身工作室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fran's converted her old bedroom into a tattoo studio of her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.97,0:10:57.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎來到幸運貓咪紋身藝術工作室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Welcome to Lucky Kitty Tattoo Arts!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.65,0:11:04.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡畫畫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, I've always drawn
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.92,0:11:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也很鐘情紋身藝術\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and I've always been interested in tattoo art,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.84,0:11:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去當過學徒  掌握了這門技術\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}so I went for an apprenticeship and I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:12.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但想在繁華街區的工作室里當個全職紋身師\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But with full-time places in high street studios
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變得越來越困難\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}increasingly hard to find,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.28,0:11:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙蘭作為一個新手紋身師\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fran's part of a new breed of tattooist,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.66,0:11:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能在家中開設工作室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}setting up at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.56,0:11:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的毫無名氣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm a no-name, really,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.09,0:11:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我需要一些東西吸引他人注意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and I needed something, you know, to stand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.90,0:11:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作室名字朗朗上口  容易令人記住\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And it's sort of a mouthful. So you sort of remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:27.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸運貓咪紋身藝術工作室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lucky Kitty Tattoo Arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:29.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是個新手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Although a relative beginner,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.31,0:11:31.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她每小時收費已達到三十英鎊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}she's already charging 30 pounds an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.45,0:11:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都很順利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's going really well,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.85,0:11:36.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我為顧客提供了與眾不同的東西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}because I think I offer something different.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.58,0:11:39.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從大的方面看來沒什么不同\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I mean, nothing different in the grand scheme of things,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.40,0:11:40.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在我們鎮上還是獨特的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but in our town.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.81,0:11:43.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在家里開設工作室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And having a studio in their house
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:46.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對她父母產生了深遠的影響\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}has made a definite impression on her parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.26,0:11:48.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我的眼睛沒以前好使了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Although my eyes aren't what they used to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.25,0:11:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是還是很漂亮  蒂奇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that's very nice, Titch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.94,0:11:53.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我也想在背后紋個仙女了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I want a fairy on my back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.71,0:11:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紋身這東西很奇怪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's a strange thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經讓她給我紋了兩個了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've actually had two now of her,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.01,0:12:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這事放在以前我想都不會想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which I would never have thought about before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.94,0:12:03.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從來不覺得自己會去紋身\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It would never have occurred to me to have a tattoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.39,0:12:06.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙蘭手藝很棒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, Fran is good. She's, er...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.25,0:12:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也許有點偏心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, I might be biased,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:09.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我應該偏心的  我是她爸呀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I will be biased, I'm her dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.05,0:12:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有被她紋過的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but all the people that she has done a tattoo for,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.15,0:12:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都非常滿意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}they've all been very, very pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.88,0:12:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來  芙蘭要給她爸爸雷設計一個新紋身\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Next, Fran's going to design a new tattoo for her dad, Ray.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都這把年紀了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}With my age now,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.39,0:12:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道還能活多少日子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know how long more I'm going to be lasting for,
