Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.56,0:45:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是還給我創收呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it might fucking help me or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.97,0:45:21.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你倒提醒了我  不能和你們出去喝酒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Remind me never to go out drinking with you guys.
