Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.54,0:45:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連馬特都開始覺得該向前看了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But even Matt is starting to think it's time to move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.50,0:45:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從阿伊納帕回來后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Since I've come home from Ayia Napa, I think it's just, like,
