Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.55,0:45:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想安定下來了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you know what I mean, I want to settle down and that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.01,0:45:42.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和家人一起度假什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Like, have family holidays and shit like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.87,0:45:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想好好休息一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I just want to chill back a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.94,0:45:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我成熟點了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, I am growing up a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.76,0:45:50.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要有自己的公寓  重新開始工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm gonna get my own flat and all that, get back into work,
