Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.75,0:45:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能再見到我的孩子們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So I can actually get to see my kids and that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.52,0:46:02.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬特還是原來的他  只是變得更懂事了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, not a new Matt, just a bit more sensible one, like.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.76,0:46:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是喜歡玩  只是更有節制了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll still have fun, but it's just have it in moderation,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.56,0:46:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如每周只玩六天而不是天天玩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}like six days a week instead of seven.
