Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.54,0:46:13.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝天謝地  開始有點疼了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank God for that, it was starting to hurt a bit then.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.70,0:46:16.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才開始疼  你剛疼得像青蛙似的上躥下跳\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Starting to hurt? You were jumping about like a box of frogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.52,0:46:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從未認真對待過生活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, I'll never, ever take life too serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.06,0:46:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你告訴我  生活的意義是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You tell me, what is the point of life?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.14,0:46:27.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活著就是生活  死了  生活就沒了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're here till we die. When we die, there is no more life,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.59,0:46:30.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以趁還活著不妨好好享樂  對不對\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}so you might as well have fun whilst you're here, innit?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.35,0:46:31.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懂了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you know what I mean?
