Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.17,0:46:35.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒不如死去  說簡單點就是這個意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that's when you might as well be dead, simple as.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.33,0:46:38.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常好  說真的  我很喜歡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Very good, fair play, I like that.
